@startuml
state "Search Filter Selection" as SearchFilter
state "Price Range Selection" as PriceRange
state "Matching Users Displayed" as MatchingUsers

[*] --> SearchFilter
SearchFilter --> PriceRange : select price range
PriceRange --> MatchingUsers : display matching users

note right of SearchFilter: allows users to search by filter category
note left of PriceRange: allows users to search by selecting a price range as a filter

MatchingUsers --> [*]

@enduml
